# Medicine Reminder System

## 📌 Description
A full-stack application that helps users manage and track their medicine schedules.

## 🚀 Features
- Add medicine reminders
- Store data using SQLite
- Simple user interface

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Python (Flask)
- HTML
- SQLite

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run backend:
python app.py

3. Open frontend:
Open index.html in browser
